{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixeria, An all-in-one Pixel MMO</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yes, you heard right. What you miss and what you wish you had met in a single universe. <strong>Create your own island</strong>, and enjoy endless adventures with those around you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/login.gif?t=1728485722\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On a deserted island, with the sky and the waves as your companions, you can <strong>become a gardener and harvest your own crops</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/customization.gif?t=1728485722\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through various missions, you can <strong>earn valuable materials and develop your character</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/beekeeping.gif?t=1728485722\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On another day when you are bored, you can <strong>take care of your animals or even beekeeping</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/extras/trade.gif?t=1728485722\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Believing that power lies in the economy, you can <strong>find your way to wealth through trading</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Knowing that the real diamonds are underground,  you can <strong>become a professional miner</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In short, <strong>you can do whatever you really want</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixeria offers you the chance to create a universe of your own choosing, making new friends and creating your best memories here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join us and enjoy unlimited adventures!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Trading</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Mining</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Farming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Ranching</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Socializing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fishing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Also Note That:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <i>You can play from anywhere, anytime</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <i>Pixeria is still in early development, join our discord to experience the beta tests.</i></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728485722","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728485722","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728485722","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368340/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728485722","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"MMO","id":20},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixeria, An all-in-on